# Generated by `tree-sitter generate` from grammar.js — do not commit.
# These files cause merge conflicts (~63K-line parser.c) when task branches
# commit them.  build.rs auto-regenerates if missing.
src/parser.c
src/grammar.json
src/node-types.json

# tree-sitter CLI binary — not needed in the repo.
/tree-sitter

# Local compiled object files from ad-hoc scanner.c builds (gcc -c, etc.).
# build.rs compiles scanner.c via cc::Build into target/<profile>/build/... ;
# any *.o sitting in the source tree is a stale artifact that would silently
# drift from scanner.c and must never be committed.
*.o
